# The entire web frontend (marketing site + web wallet) now lives in the PRIVATE
# cereblix-ops repo. This public repo is ONLY the coin/protocol (node, miner,
# wallet CLI, core, neuromorph, stratum, wasm, hiveos). web/ is kept locally as
# working files for deploy, but not tracked / published here.
web/
otc/
nacl.min.js

# Forum announcement (ANN) drafts + banner - marketing, kept local-only
ann/
tmp_rel/

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Regenerable build noise & vendored toolchains (added 2026-06-30)
# These trees are large + regenerable and were poisoning grep/agent search
# (~33k files). They stay ON DISK — in active use for builds — and are only
# IGNORED here, never deleted. Compiled binaries are already covered above by
# `*.exe`, `bin/`, and `release/`; the block below adds the rest.
# CAREFUL: this intentionally does NOT touch real source — desktop/*.go,
# desktop/frontend/js, desktop/frontend/css, and wallet-android/.../app/src
# all remain tracked.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Vendored Go toolchain (go.exe lives here; regenerable from the go1.25 download)
toolchain/go/

# Vendored Zig cross-compiler used by the nmminer C build (regenerable download)
components/nmminer/zig-windows-*/

# Go build / module cache
.gocache/

# Node / npm dependency trees, at any depth
**/node_modules/

# Desktop (Wails) wallet: build output + Wails-generated JS bindings.
# (KEEP desktop/*.go, desktop/frontend/js, desktop/frontend/css — real source.)
desktop/build/
desktop/frontend/wailsjs/

# Android (gomobile + Gradle) wallet: build output, Gradle cache, machine-local
# SDK config, and the gomobile-generated AAR/JAR (regenerated by `gomobile bind`).
# (KEEP wallet-android/android-app/app/src + wallet-android/mobile — real source.)
wallet-android/android-app/app/build/
wallet-android/**/.gradle/
wallet-android/android-app/local.properties
wallet-android/android-app/app/libs/*.aar
wallet-android/android-app/app/libs/*.jar

# Scratch / staging build dir
staging/
